WEBVTT

00:01:18.139 --> 00:01:19.940
The style of this Ceremonial Robe is quite unique.

00:01:20.139 --> 00:01:21.780
Why doesn't the Noble Consort try it on?

00:01:22.180 --> 00:01:23.419
Let us feast our eyes.

00:01:24.180 --> 00:01:25.540
Your Highness, please try it.

00:01:25.780 --> 00:01:26.859
This robe is magnificent.

00:01:27.100 --> 00:01:29.179
Only Your Highness's grace can match it.

00:01:29.460 --> 00:01:31.659
You will surely look radiant in it.

00:01:41.580 --> 00:01:43.220
The one who wants to harm Wan'er...

00:01:44.379 --> 00:01:45.659
Could it be Concubine Cao?

00:01:47.779 --> 00:01:48.739
I remember...

00:01:48.900 --> 00:01:50.339
I've seen Serpent's Tongue Herb here before.

00:01:50.940 --> 00:01:51.940
Its roots...

00:01:51.940 --> 00:01:53.540
can neutralize the toxicity of purple corydalis pollen.

00:01:56.580 --> 00:01:58.339
This was meant for my sister to wear.

00:01:59.860 --> 00:02:00.900
Seeing it makes me miss her.

00:02:01.180 --> 00:02:02.900
I have made a spectacle of myself before you all.

00:02:03.459 --> 00:02:04.979
Yinsheng, take it away for now.

00:02:04.979 --> 00:02:05.620
Yes.

00:02:05.620 --> 00:02:06.419
Hold on.

00:02:13.180 --> 00:02:14.500
The great affairs of the state...

00:02:14.580 --> 00:02:15.739
lie in sacrifice and war.

00:02:16.259 --> 00:02:18.539
The Noble Consort is so frail, a mere gust could topple her.

00:02:18.819 --> 00:02:21.259
I fear she cannot handle the Imperial Sericulture Rite.

00:02:21.539 --> 00:02:24.179
Why not let me take over?

00:02:29.980 --> 00:02:32.459
The Imperial Sericulture Rite has always been the Empress's duty.

00:02:33.099 --> 00:02:34.739
My eldest sister has just passed away.

00:02:35.179 --> 00:02:37.500
If I were to hand this rite over to another,

00:02:37.700 --> 00:02:39.060
how could I face her?

00:02:40.259 --> 00:02:41.420
The Empress has passed.

00:02:42.140 --> 00:02:43.860
And the Noble Consort is in poor health.

00:02:44.220 --> 00:02:46.220
I am merely thinking of the greater good.

00:02:50.340 --> 00:02:52.539
Let go! This is the Noble Consort's Ceremonial Robe.

00:02:55.899 --> 00:02:56.700
Noble Consort Meng,

00:02:58.099 --> 00:02:59.220
this is against protocol.

00:03:09.259 --> 00:03:10.739
How dare you, you lowly maid!

00:03:13.340 --> 00:03:14.259
Your Highness, please understand.

00:03:14.459 --> 00:03:15.940
Director Chen specifically instructed...

00:03:16.220 --> 00:03:18.060
that the Ceremonial Robe must not pass into other hands.

00:03:23.140 --> 00:03:23.860
You lowly wretch!

00:03:24.420 --> 00:03:25.219
Am I lesser than...

00:03:25.219 --> 00:03:26.820
a mere director of the Bureau of Imperial Attire?

00:03:27.540 --> 00:03:28.339
Slap her mouth!

00:03:29.939 --> 00:03:30.899
Your Highness, please quell your anger.

00:03:31.100 --> 00:03:33.700
This Ceremonial Robe was tailored for the Noble Consort.

00:03:33.899 --> 00:03:35.380
I fear it may not fit Your Highness.

00:03:35.499 --> 00:03:36.739
Please allow the Bureau of Imperial Attire...

00:03:36.739 --> 00:03:38.459
to sew a new Ceremonial Robe for Your Highness.

00:03:40.580 --> 00:03:42.860
That is a sensible thing to say.

00:03:46.179 --> 00:03:47.619
Then, as you suggest,

00:03:47.860 --> 00:03:49.700
rush to make a new set for me.

00:03:50.179 --> 00:03:51.700
Yes, this slave obeys.

00:03:52.660 --> 00:03:53.860
Since there is nothing else,

00:03:53.939 --> 00:03:55.420
I shall take my leave.

00:03:58.140 --> 00:03:59.459
Your subject takes her leave.

00:04:05.580 --> 00:04:07.100
Don't dirty our Orchid and Angelica Palace.

00:04:07.619 --> 00:04:08.860
Hurry up and scurry back,

00:04:08.899 --> 00:04:10.260
and go rush that new robe for Noble Consort Meng.

00:04:10.260 --> 00:04:10.779
Yinsheng.

00:04:10.779 --> 00:04:11.420
Yes.

00:04:11.459 --> 00:04:12.179
Let it be.

00:04:12.380 --> 00:04:13.939
My dispute with Noble Consort Meng...

00:04:13.939 --> 00:04:16.019
does not lie in whom a palace maid chooses.

00:04:16.619 --> 00:04:17.779
Do not make things difficult for her.

00:04:23.059 --> 00:04:24.339
Your Highness is gentle and kind.

00:04:24.939 --> 00:04:26.619
If the Empress were still here,

00:04:27.300 --> 00:04:28.820
she surely would not let you suffer such grievances.

00:04:28.820 --> 00:04:29.540
Yinsheng.

00:04:30.179 --> 00:04:32.019
I am ultimately not like my sister.

00:04:35.179 --> 00:04:36.260
I am weary.

00:04:36.380 --> 00:04:37.339
Let us return to the bedchamber.

00:04:37.820 --> 00:04:38.619
Yes.

00:04:44.580 --> 00:04:45.380
You may rise.

00:04:48.420 --> 00:04:49.619
Noble Consort, please understand.

00:04:49.660 --> 00:04:51.739
This slave only acted out of expediency just now.

00:04:51.899 --> 00:04:53.660
I had no intention of currying favor with Noble Consort Meng.

00:04:54.499 --> 00:04:55.300
It matters not.

00:04:57.339 --> 00:04:58.700
Why is your face dirty?

00:05:01.100 --> 00:05:01.860
Wipe it off.

00:05:02.179 --> 00:05:02.899
I bestow this upon you.

00:05:06.939 --> 00:05:07.860
Thank you, Your Highness.

00:05:12.499 --> 00:05:14.939
The one behind the mourning hall fire has not been found.

00:05:15.660 --> 00:05:16.739
If I rashly reveal my identity,

00:05:17.339 --> 00:05:19.339
I fear I might drag Wan'er into this dangerous game.

00:05:21.140 --> 00:05:22.459
It is better to use the identity of Feng Qing,

00:05:22.459 --> 00:05:23.380
lurk in the shadows,

00:05:23.779 --> 00:05:24.860
and wait for the right moment to strike.

00:05:27.379 --> 00:05:29.460
Though we sisters cannot acknowledge each other for now,

00:05:30.579 --> 00:05:32.220
the Imperial Sericulture Rite that belongs to you...

00:05:32.860 --> 00:05:33.660
Your sister...

00:05:34.579 --> 00:05:35.939
will surely win it back for you.

00:05:44.020 --> 00:05:45.460
His Majesty returns to the palace!

00:05:45.699 --> 00:05:47.100
Make way!

00:06:20.379 --> 00:06:23.619
This is the bracelet Your Majesty put on me with your own hands

00:06:24.900 --> 00:06:27.059
I thought it held Your Majesty's love

00:06:27.540 --> 00:06:29.139
So I wore it day and night

00:06:30.059 --> 00:06:31.100
But I never imagined

00:06:32.900 --> 00:06:34.900
That it actually contained musk

00:06:36.780 --> 00:06:38.900
If I hadn't broken the bracelet today

00:06:39.660 --> 00:06:42.100
I fear I would have been kept in the dark for a lifetime

00:06:43.059 --> 00:06:43.939
Why?

00:06:47.540 --> 00:06:49.220
I will tell you the reason in time

00:06:49.420 --> 00:06:50.100
Fine

00:06:50.660 --> 00:06:51.699
Then let me say it

00:06:53.739 --> 00:06:56.020
Because Your Majesty is wary of the Gu Family

00:06:56.259 --> 00:06:57.660
Because my surname is Gu

00:06:58.179 --> 00:06:59.100
Because Your Majesty dares not

00:06:59.100 --> 00:07:01.499
Let a Gu Empress bear a royal heir

00:07:03.780 --> 00:07:06.179
Do you think we are in a position to have heirs now?

00:07:06.699 --> 00:07:07.980
If you were to give birth to an heir

00:07:08.139 --> 00:07:09.860
Is it to let the Gu family threaten Me?

00:07:09.860 --> 00:07:11.939
Or do you want to rule from behind the curtain like the Empress Dowager?

00:07:13.420 --> 00:07:15.179
I can't believe Your Majesty thinks so

00:07:16.819 --> 00:07:17.460
Fine

00:07:20.059 --> 00:07:21.220
It seems Your Majesty

00:07:22.100 --> 00:07:25.020
Never saw me as someone to walk side by side with

00:07:30.939 --> 00:07:33.059
The past is all but a dream

00:07:34.379 --> 00:07:35.780
Since I have a second chance

00:07:36.939 --> 00:07:39.259
I will never endure in silence like before

00:07:44.300 --> 00:07:45.579
The board is set

00:07:46.059 --> 00:07:47.259
A hundred stones wait to be played

00:07:48.100 --> 00:07:49.780
Even if it is a losing game

00:07:50.739 --> 00:07:52.699
I will make my move to break the deadlock

00:07:56.420 --> 00:07:58.579
I wonder how thoroughly the mourning hall was burned

00:07:58.579 --> 00:07:58.980
Right

00:07:58.980 --> 00:08:00.900
If we can find the late Empress's jewelry

00:08:00.900 --> 00:08:02.059
We'll be rich

00:08:13.340 --> 00:08:15.139
Coveting the Empress's relics

00:08:16.220 --> 00:08:17.579
Disrespecting the Empress

00:08:17.939 --> 00:08:18.819
Darn it

00:08:47.900 --> 00:08:49.980
I thought returning to the capital to mourn my aunt

00:08:51.020 --> 00:08:52.660
Would allow me to see you again

00:08:56.100 --> 00:08:57.900
But after traveling hundreds of miles day and night

00:08:59.300 --> 00:09:01.619
All that awaited me was a handful of your cold ashes

00:09:03.100 --> 00:09:03.939
Sister

00:09:05.300 --> 00:09:07.460
We haven't seen each other for five years

00:09:08.100 --> 00:09:09.660
Why didn't you wait for me?

00:09:40.259 --> 00:09:41.819
Frost silk is incredibly sharp

00:09:42.620 --> 00:09:44.380
It is rarely used in ordinary embroidery

00:09:45.420 --> 00:09:47.859
Why would it appear in the fire of the mourning hall?

00:10:00.339 --> 00:10:01.140
Little darling.

00:10:01.339 --> 00:10:03.020
What took you so long to return?

00:10:03.579 --> 00:10:04.979
Let go! What are you doing?

00:10:05.140 --> 00:10:06.260
This is the palace maids' quarters.

00:10:07.380 --> 00:10:08.819
Maids' quarters, is it?

00:10:09.579 --> 00:10:10.780
The Bureau of Imperial Attire...

00:10:10.979 --> 00:10:13.059
...has always been my territory.

00:10:13.059 --> 00:10:14.260
I came here this time...

00:10:14.339 --> 00:10:16.020
...specifically to find you.

00:10:17.179 --> 00:10:18.260
Of all the past Chiefs of the Bureau...

00:10:18.459 --> 00:10:20.059
...only one started as a eunuch.

00:10:20.140 --> 00:10:20.939
His surname was Sun.

00:10:21.059 --> 00:10:22.459
Later, he rose to the Directorate of Ceremonial.

00:10:22.459 --> 00:10:23.219
My Lord.

00:10:23.500 --> 00:10:24.859
Please let go of this servant.

00:10:24.939 --> 00:10:26.699
Since My Lord came looking for me...

00:10:26.900 --> 00:10:29.260
...why not sit up high...

00:10:29.339 --> 00:10:31.459
...and let this servant serve you properly?

00:10:32.620 --> 00:10:35.020
Director Chen said you'd come around.

00:10:36.300 --> 00:10:38.459
Indeed, after dying once...

00:10:39.059 --> 00:10:41.140
...you are reborn.

00:10:42.300 --> 00:10:44.459
So Eunuch Sun colluded with Director Chen...

00:10:44.500 --> 00:10:45.699
...planning to defile Feng Qing.

00:10:46.660 --> 00:10:48.059
No wonder she wanted to end her life.

00:10:50.260 --> 00:10:51.099
My Lord.

00:10:51.380 --> 00:10:52.819
This servant has a trick.

00:10:53.179 --> 00:10:54.300
I wonder if My Lord...

00:10:55.500 --> 00:10:56.859
...would like to try it?

00:10:57.819 --> 00:10:58.459
Try.

00:10:59.380 --> 00:11:00.620
Must try it.

00:11:01.979 --> 00:11:02.859
The moment I walked in...

00:11:02.859 --> 00:11:04.699
...I smelled you, you little minx...

00:11:04.819 --> 00:11:06.140
...that scent on your body...

00:11:06.140 --> 00:11:07.420
...that slutty smell.

00:11:11.979 --> 00:11:13.339
Don't rush, My Lord.

00:11:14.380 --> 00:11:15.339
Careful...

00:11:16.219 --> 00:11:17.500
...or you'll spoil the fun.

00:11:18.260 --> 00:11:19.140
What is this?

00:11:19.140 --> 00:11:20.219
What kind of move is this?

00:11:27.780 --> 00:11:29.660
Why can't I see anything?

00:11:30.300 --> 00:11:31.339
Do you like it?

00:11:31.620 --> 00:11:32.500
I like it.

00:11:33.740 --> 00:11:35.140
With strangulation...

00:11:36.059 --> 00:11:37.819
...one must not use sudden force.

00:11:46.540 --> 00:11:48.140
You lowly maid! How dare you!

00:11:49.059 --> 00:11:50.099
In this palace...

00:11:50.500 --> 00:11:52.459
...there is nothing This Palace dares not do.

00:11:52.699 --> 00:11:53.540
This Palace?

00:11:53.939 --> 00:11:54.740
You are...

00:11:58.660 --> 00:12:00.740
Eunuch Sun, corrupt in office...

00:12:00.979 --> 00:12:02.179
...committing adultery in the palace...

00:12:02.300 --> 00:12:03.459
...violating palace rules.

00:12:03.699 --> 00:12:05.099
Immediate execution by strangulation.

00:12:05.420 --> 00:12:08.059
This Palace will give you a quick death.

00:12:32.780 --> 00:12:34.260
In the eyes of This Palace...

00:12:34.859 --> 00:12:36.260
...there is no revenge in the next life...

00:12:37.740 --> 00:12:39.500
...only retribution in this one.

00:12:56.140 --> 00:12:57.859
All these years I served as a military doctor...

00:12:58.179 --> 00:12:59.699
...saving countless soldiers...

00:13:00.540 --> 00:13:02.660
...yet I could not save you, trapped in these walls.

00:13:04.099 --> 00:13:04.819
Sister.

00:13:05.500 --> 00:13:06.579
The Imperial Family is heartless.

00:13:07.780 --> 00:13:08.819
If there is a next life...

00:13:09.219 --> 00:13:10.660
...may you become a crane amidst the clouds...

00:13:11.059 --> 00:13:12.459
...no longer trapped in this cage.

00:13:26.740 --> 00:13:27.740
When I left the capital...

00:13:28.339 --> 00:13:29.660
...the sachet you gave me...

00:13:29.660 --> 00:13:31.179
...I have kept with me every single day.

00:13:31.780 --> 00:13:33.300
I never imagined that parting...

00:13:34.260 --> 00:13:35.819
...would be our final farewell.

00:13:43.819 --> 00:13:44.620
Sister...

00:13:45.579 --> 00:13:47.219
If anyone persecuted you...

00:13:48.660 --> 00:13:50.740
...even if I must trample the ninefold palace...

00:13:51.219 --> 00:13:53.339
...I will bury the entire harem with you.

00:14:57.939 --> 00:14:58.740
A Xuan.

00:14:59.140 --> 00:15:00.420
Shouldn't he be in the military camp?

00:15:00.859 --> 00:15:01.819
Looking at your attire...

00:15:01.819 --> 00:15:03.059
...you must be from the Bureau of Imperial Attire.

00:15:03.500 --> 00:15:04.459
A mere palace maid...

00:15:04.459 --> 00:15:05.859
...dares to kill in the middle of the night...

00:15:05.859 --> 00:15:07.059
...and dump the body in a well?

00:15:07.500 --> 00:15:08.740
Do you know that is a capital crime?

00:15:09.260 --> 00:15:10.540
Looking at your attire...

00:15:10.540 --> 00:15:11.819
...you are not from the palace.

00:15:12.300 --> 00:15:15.099
An outsider man in the harem during curfew...

00:15:15.140 --> 00:15:17.140
...do you know that is also a capital crime?

00:15:17.219 --> 00:15:19.059
This little maid is not flustered at all...

00:15:19.059 --> 00:15:20.260
...and even retorts.

00:15:21.020 --> 00:15:23.260
Should I acknowledge A Xuan?

00:15:23.699 --> 00:15:24.979
Since you discovered me...

00:15:25.099 --> 00:15:26.260
...I might as well do as you did...

00:15:26.620 --> 00:15:27.780
...and silence the witness.